Commit Message:
Make exception creation more flexible

This may have been crashing in several cases, but it's difficult to tell.
Do not throw on new attributes/properties

Add set_uses_idfa method

There is currently an asconnect bug where it ignores the `usesIdfa` attribute if you set it when creating the app. To work around it, call this new `set_uses_idfa` after creation.
Add retry logic to get for 401 error (#8)
Use tokens for only 10 minutes at most

Reduce max age of tokens from 20 minutes to 15 minutes

I suspect that we are hitting a clock skew bug with 20 minutes where Apple doesn't think that the token is valid since it can't be more than 20 minutes old.
Retry on 401 auth issue for upload
Add retry on submitting for review
